title: Preston, Lancashire - Wikipedia
snippet: Preston (/ ˈprɛstən / ⓘ) is a city on the north bank of the River Ribble in Lancashire, in North West England. The city is the administrative centre of the county of Lancashire and the wider City of Preston local government district.
